    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: Content is presented using a variety of textual and structural formats. The "Rulers & Legends" section uses cards to detail the stories of each king, including the famous tale of the master thief and the pyramid builders. "Great Egyptian Works" uses a clear, grid-based layout to highlight the scale of the Labyrinth and Lake Moeris. "The Rise of Amasis" and "Amasis & The Greeks" sections use descriptive cards to detail the political intrigue and the king's character and policies. All content is static, designed for direct consumption, and all graphics are created with structured HTML and CSS to avoid any SVG or Mermaid JS. -->
